      <title>Robinhood 推出信用卡，进一步推动交易之外的业务</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-26/robinhood-unveils-credit-card-in-further-push-beyond-trading</link>
      <description><![CDATA[Robinhood Markets Inc. 以提供免佣金交易而闻名，该公司正在向美国消费者推出信用卡，以期成为一家更广泛的金融服务公司。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-26/robinhood-unveils-credit-card-in-further-push-beyond-trading</guid>
